node.title: Man charged with attempted murder after woman stabbed near Taup≈ç
node.description: He will appear in court on Monday.
node.content: ["Police have charged a man with attempted murder after the stabbing of a woman in\u00a0Taup\u014d district on Sunday afternoon.", "According to Detective Senior Sergeant Craig Rawlinson, a 49-year-old Auckland man is due to appear in the Rotorua District Court on Monday in relation to the stabbing in Motutere at about 12:30pm on Sunday.", "He has been charged with attempted murder, wounding with intent to cause grievous bodily harm and aggravated assault.", "The woman is currently in a critical condition in Waikato Hospital."]
